\id 1JN - Sembeleke SAMBERIGI PNG 1 JOHN 01 12/02/91 MACNAUGHTAN
\h 1 DIONI
\toc1 Dionimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\toc2 1 Dioni
\toc3 1 Dioni
\mt1 Dionimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\c 1
\s1 Panake Pi
\p 
\v 1 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ kini pitolo hataęž‰ pa hao hao halaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ pinaęž‰ pi kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ laasomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ opolomaęž‰ make otaęž‰ nikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me. Otaęž‰e. Nikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handolomaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ otaęž‰ wataalomaęž‰me.
\v 2 Hande Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do kenkemaęž‰ handolo polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ peneme yamo epeeke handa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handomaęž‰me. Kutupa koto mo Ateke yaapo hao hayeke niki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaeyaęž‰ Deto halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolome.
\v 3 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaa opolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make opuaasomaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Ateke make ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke Yesu Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± hone homeke ulumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ apaęž‰tamenaęž‰yeke lomaęž‰me.
\v 4 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ doeki laasomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ tumbulu baenaęž‰yeke pitolomaęž‰me.
\s1 Kodaęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±e
\p 
\v 5 Ametaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ opolomaęž‰ ekimanu iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ opuaaseme ekitaęž‰ doe. Kodaęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± kone yaalo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 6 Kotaęž‰ koto yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± homeke hone ulumaęž‰me la alo hataęž‰ pa homeke dinaęž‰ kone timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ pi alomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ makeaasaęž‰ hau pitolomaęž‰ make yayapikieki pitolomaęž‰me.
\v 7 Pate mo ipikitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ niki make mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hao polumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ hone homeke u alualu polomaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke Yesunaęž‰ wemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hokeeki paeyao wamo peaasaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 8 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alo hataęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ hokeeki na ulaęž‰me lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ kone makeaasomaęž‰me. Kutupa niki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰eki na ulaęž‰me.
\v 9 Pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke haumanu Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kelepomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pulueke laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki pilieke. Kutupa otaęž‰ tikitiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitolo hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyao paeyaasotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hokeeki polomaęž‰eki paeyao wamo pealieke.
\v 10 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alo hataęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ hoke hau na polomaęž‰me la lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki pi lo halaęž‰ hali au laasomaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.
\c 2
\s1 Ketisotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali
\p 
\v 1 Yaka wekiwandiki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hokeeki na pulu peleme tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ doeki iki paęž‰taęž‰ laasome. Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ hokeeki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hau peaaso hataęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ honke lawaasaęž‰ some maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ tikitiki piki some Yesu Ketiso halaęž‰me.
\v 2 Kutupa Ketisotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau paeyawalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tekee. Nikaęž‰ hoke hau homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa paeyao sikinaęž‰ hoke hau make loaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 3 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki handolomaęž‰me laa nikaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me.
\v 4 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki handolota alo kone ipikaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu na opua piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ yayapiki pi alaęž‰ some make mo otaęž‰ pi alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.
\v 5 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua puaęž‰tiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puki halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ handaa ulaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni polomaęž‰me laa hone uluekemaęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki dupa.
\v 6 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halome leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ pieke tupaęž‰ kone hao peliaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Panake pi ulaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 7 Yaka pukipiki yankeke tonuo. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do laaso pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ panakeeki diaęž‰me. Mo kini pitolo hataęž‰ hande ambaęž‰ wia haeme pi ulaęž‰eki konee. Koto ambaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande opeleme ekimanue.
\v 8 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ ame do laaso pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ panakeekie. Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ make handolomaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ mo timbaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ lombei pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo otaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 9 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halome alo kone ipikaęž‰ kame honditi piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ame do make timbaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ ha pelia halaęž‰me.
\v 10 Pate mandaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pu tialo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.
\v 11 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke honditi piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pominolo hataęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ leke holu pealaęž‰ ekiyalo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pulaęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ hone na ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 12 Yaka wekiwandikio. Mo Ketisonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ ambaęž‰ paeyawalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi laasome.
\v 13 Yaka apaęž‰titio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi laaso ekitaęž‰ pa mo otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ kini pea aęž‰pa pa hao halaęž‰ sometaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wilimi ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Panake haliweki iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi laasome. Paa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Hoke Temoko bepolaleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 14 Yaka wekiwandikio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi laaso ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ handa hone wilimi ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Yaka apaęž‰titio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi laaso ekitaęž‰ pa mo otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ kini pea aęž‰pa paa hao halaęž‰ sometaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wilimi ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Panake haliweki iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi laaso ekitaęž‰ pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi iki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokolo haenaęž‰ iki honkopu hasememe. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Hoke Temoko bepolaleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 15 Do kenkenaęž‰ hau o do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homelememe.
\v 16 Do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ pa mo lopa halaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handolo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaa biki tieke wiaasaęž‰ alemanu make koto ale paeyao siki homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto hau paeyaonaęž‰ teketaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ekie.
\v 17 Kutupa do kenke make do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paeyao make koto alemanu paeyao sikitaęž‰ paetaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki peaasaęž‰ sometaęž‰ hoto paeyao daęž‰ta hao halieke.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki hali
\p 
\v 18 Yaka wekiwandikio. Paetolo natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰e. Mo Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki hali ipilieke laataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ ta opuaeyaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki tapake wopu ambaęž‰ opolo epelememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ paetolo natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa nikaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me.
\v 19 Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ nikaęž‰ homhomeke hone wia mombololomaęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰pate pa na apaęž‰taememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki minaęž‰paęž‰lalememe. Iki aęž‰ndaęž‰ nikaęž‰ mombololomaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰taemekenaęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ halo pimime. Pate ikaęž‰ pa minaęž‰paęž‰laemeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo niki ameĚ±leĚ± na apaęž‰talemeeki peneme yaasememe.
\p 
\v 20 Kutu pimipate pa ya wekiwandikio. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande Ketisomaęž‰ kuaęž‰nealaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi ambaęž‰ koto miniki halememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wilimime.
\v 21 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ laaso ekitaęž‰ pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki hone na wilimiki yeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo hone wilimiki handa pueme. Kutupa make mo yayapikieki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na ipulaęž‰me laataęž‰ hone ikaęž‰ wilimiki puaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo yayapiki pi alaęž‰ sometaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Pa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Ketiso diaęž‰me alaęž‰ some lataa. Dupiki sometaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki somee. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Ateke make Eiyeke make hoki walaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 23 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo Eiyeke hoki waleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ateke make hoki walaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Eiyeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ateke make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ mo hande titinaęž‰ kini pitolo hataęž‰ opimi pi ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ mondu hapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ koto opimi pi pa u haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo Eiyeke pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ateke yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± hoto paeyao taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halimikie.
\v 25 Kototaęž‰ mo hande Ketisomaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ kulueke laa pi laęž‰ wiaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki lataa.
\p 
\v 26 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do laaso ekitaęž‰ mo iki makealuekemaęž‰ taapeleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ do laaso handaęž‰e.
\v 27 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidi ambaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidi iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰ pelia haenaęž‰taęž‰ iki walaęž‰peke some maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ weiyaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyao walieke. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ yayapikieki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ekie. Koto ekinaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰eki opua pitolo hataęž‰ make Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pu pelia hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 28 Otaęž‰e. Yaka wekiwandikio. Ipiki yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hapee. Pa ekipeke ipiki opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ honkopu haasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ tumbulu paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutupa koto mo ipiliaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki handolo hataęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homolo polome tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 29 Ketisotaęž‰ tikitiki paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone wilimime. Kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi ameda tikitiki piki hau pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandikie laataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone witolo pelememe.
\c 3
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki
\p 
\v 1 Mo Apaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki tieke handaęž‰pe. Ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke aneke yalo hataęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki lelememe. Kotaęž‰ koto ekinaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikie. Doeki tekenaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ na handelemeeki yalo niki make na handelememe.
\v 2 Otaęž‰ yaka taęž‰maęž‰ni sunuo. Nikitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo wetepenaęž‰ halo polome ekitaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na peneme yaalaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo Ketiso opolo ipiliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ ipikimaęž‰ kone handulumeke. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halaęž‰eki nikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handolo polome ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 3 Peaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki hone puao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰ mo Ketisotaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±lolo hataęž‰ pa yako peaa halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipiki make haĚ±iĚ± peaamaęž‰naęž‰ pa yako peatiki pu halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 4 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ hoke hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke hoke hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekie.
\v 5 Ketiso opolo epeeke ekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau mea bawaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me laa hone wilimime.
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi Ketiso yaapo hone homeke wia taęž‰maęž‰ni pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ hoke hau pa na pu halaęž‰me. Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ hoke hau pa putia peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ Ketiso otaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰ make hone na ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 7 Yaka wekiwandikio. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki na makeaenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo Ketiso paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ tikitiki piki some halaęž‰me.
\v 8 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ hoke hau pa putia peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo Hoke Temokonaęž‰eki halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Hoke Temokomaęž‰taęž‰ kini pitolo kone hoke hau paęž‰leke loaęž‰me. Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ doeki tekenaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Hoke Temokomaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 9 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hoke hau pa na putia pu halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ yaalo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau pa putia puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 10 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki pitaęž‰ mo Hoke Temokonaęž‰ wekiwandiki yaapo ataęž‰kaęž‰ tieke paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ hau na pu o ipikaęž‰ yankeke pukimaęž‰ na homo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ weki na halaęž‰me.
\s1 Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 11 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande kini pitolo hataęž‰ titinaęž‰ opimi pitaęž‰ doe. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 12 Nikitaęž‰ mo hande Keinimaęž‰ na hando hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Hoke Temokonaęž‰eki hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke Eipolo kone lu homaeyekeme. Pa ekipeke lu homaeyekepe. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Mo ipikaęž‰ pieke hau manutaęž‰ tikitiki na pitolo haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hamekenaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ tikitiki pikieki yaalo piekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka kame tonuo. Do kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki honditi piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na penkilipaęž‰tia pomiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 14 Mo homaęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰lao daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ epolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me. Koto mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kametonu paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone ulume laa loaęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ honkopu oto paęž‰taęž‰ paa halaęž‰me.
\v 15 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke honditi piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ hali lu homaasaęž‰ somee. Kutupa ikaęž‰ hone wilimimaęž‰ mo hali lu homaasaęž‰ sometaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 16 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa hone witolomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ anketeke mea ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ haleaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make nikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ kametonu tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ pa halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 17 Mo hamoko halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ kone hameke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki na haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekieki pea ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolome laa leliepe.
\v 18 Yaka wekiwandikio. Nikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kakemaęž‰ homeke o pimaęž‰ homeke lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Diaęž‰me. Koto pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ pa mo otaęž‰eki peneme yaenaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ homekee.
\v 19 Kotaęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ tunaalomaęž‰me laa hone ulumeke. Kutupa dupitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokopolomaęž‰ ekie.
\v 20 Pate nikaęž‰ hone tekemaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hoke hau polomaęž‰me leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Kodaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone paeyaonaęž‰ aneke hali yaalo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao hone ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka pukipiki taęž‰maęž‰ni sunuo. Nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ niki hoke hau na polomaęž‰me leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokopolomaęž‰me.
\v 22 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pitolo make ipiki taęž‰naęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaasaęž‰ haumanu pua halomeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke laęž‰laęž‰ alemanu mu halomaęž‰me.
\v 23 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo niki paęž‰taęž‰ pipee alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ make pa mo hande Yesumaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ kone niki ameĚ±leĚ± pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke.
\v 24 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo tunao halaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki yaapo tunao halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ Sipitidi kaęž‰leketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± tunao halaęž‰me hone ulumaęž‰me.
\c 4
\s1 Mo otaęž‰ Sipitidi pitaęž‰ yayapiki sipitidimanu
\p 
\v 1 Yaka pukipiki taęž‰maęž‰ni sunuo. Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi molomaęž‰me aleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaake pa ikaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe laa ambaęž‰la handaa handaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo makeaaso potopede hali paeyaotaęž‰ mo kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pelemeke loaęž‰me.
\v 2 Dotaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa handaęž‰ ulu peleme tupaęž‰taęž‰ dupae. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hali aęž‰pa hayekeme laa leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ Sipitidi pilaęž‰mee.
\v 3 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ kotoeki na paęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ Sipitidi na pilaęž‰me. Koto some paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ sipitiditaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki some paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekitaęž‰ ipiliekee laataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ koto opimitaa. Kutupa ametaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ambaęž‰ koto aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰taa.
\p 
\v 4 Pate yaka wekiwandikio. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ekie. Kutupa mo makeaaso potopede manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ bepolalememe. Pa ekipeke mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ sipitidi tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ wele wopu pikieki pileke loaęž‰me.
\v 5 Hande makeaasaęž‰ potopede manumaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ pi hotu halememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kenke haunaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke haunaęž‰ tapake haleme ekiyalo koto pi opu halememe.
\v 6 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki halomaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone ulaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ pi opu halememe. Pate Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone na ulaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ pi na opilimikie. Kotaęž‰ koto hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Sipitidi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa make mo yayapiki ekinaęž‰ sipitidi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa make nikanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ tekili pea handaęž‰ u hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Kodaęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 7 Yaka taęž‰maęž‰ni tonuo. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hamanaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰e. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke halaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 8 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ekie.
\v 9 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Weki homeke do kenkenaęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki peneme yaalaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miomono yeke paęž‰laęž‰mee.
\v 10 Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homomeke handa diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki tapaalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau paeyao paeyawalaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 11 Yaka taęž‰maęž‰ni tonuo. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikitaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke aleo.
\v 12 Homekesiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰pate pa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu homomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao pitaalaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 13 Nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halomaęž‰ make ipikitaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidi kaęž‰laęž‰mee.
\v 14 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa mo Atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ some tapaalaęž‰me laa maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰tiki pu halomaęž‰me.
\v 15 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰me.
\v 16 Kutupa mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ hone tulaalomaęž‰me.
\p Kodaęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ekie. Koto ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰me.
\v 17 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Pi Yokaalu Pilie Natenaęž‰taęž‰ pa honkopu hao halo poluekemaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ ankulao pitaalaęž‰me. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ miniki halumekee. Pa ekipeke nikaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hao peolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone handaęž‰leke loaęž‰me.
\v 18 Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki na ulaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ tikitiki piki pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo paalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki pendulu baasaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao na pitaalaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke paalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hoke yenki paęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰taleke loaęž‰me.
\v 19 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki ambaęž‰la pukimaęž‰ homeeke handaa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homo halomaęž‰me.
\v 20 Kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolome alo hataęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ kame honditi piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ yayapiki pi alaęž‰ somee. Pa ekipeke mo ipikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰ kametaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homolo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 21 Mo hande Ketisomaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me la laęž‰laęž‰me.
\c 5
\s1 Kenke hau bepolalomaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 1 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Ketisoe laa hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke halaęž‰me. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 2 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo make ipikaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pu halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki make pukimaęž‰ homolomaęž‰me laa pa handolomaęž‰me.
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki opua pitolomaęž‰eki konee. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaasaęž‰me.
\v 4 Paa ekipeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ bepolapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa nikaęž‰ hone tulaalomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hau bepolatia pu halomaęž‰me.
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hau bepolaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Mo Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee laa hone tulaasaęž‰ somemaęž‰ homekee.
\s1 Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ wekitisimanu
\p 
\v 6 Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ mo ikalimaęž‰ bapitaisi pitaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ we holo pieke haunaęž‰ make epeekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo ikalinaęž‰ hau homekenaęž‰ na epeekepate pa mo ikali pitaęž‰ we yaapo telipunaęž‰naęž‰ epeekeme. Kutupa mo Sipitidimaęž‰ kone peneme yaasotaęž‰ do hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ekie laa alaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Sipitiditaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekie.
\v 7 Do ekinaęž‰ wekitisi haasaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ tepoe.
\v 8 Mo Sipitidi make mo ikali make mo we make koto hau tepomaęž‰taęž‰ homeke peneme yaasaęž‰ pi kone alememe.
\v 9 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do kenke halinaęž‰ peneme yao alaęž‰ pi hone tulao halomaęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu wotu halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto mo Eiyekenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ leeke ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki pi alaęž‰ somee alaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke koto somemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki hone na tulaalaęž‰me loaęž‰me.
\v 11 Mo peneme yao alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ doe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰eki kaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa do daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyekee.
\v 12 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo Eiyeke maĚ±ęž‰naęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki u halaęž‰pate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke na maĚ±ęž‰naęž‰laęž‰ some ipikitaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki na wia halaęž‰me.
\s1 Daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do laaso ekitaęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ melememe laa hone uemenaęž‰yeke pitolome. Koto mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me
\v 14 Nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ honkopu moĚ±lomaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ honke lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ opitaęž‰laęž‰me laa nikaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me.
\v 15 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke laęž‰tiki pu halomaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opu halaęž‰me hone ulaęž‰me. Kutupa koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekie laa hone umaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alemanu honke laęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ ku halaęž‰me hone ulumaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 16 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hamekemaęž‰ mo homenaęž‰ na laęž‰laęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo somenaęž‰eki Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki daęž‰taenaęž‰ lelieke. Koto hautaęž‰ pa mo homenaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me. Pate mo homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku polo paęž‰laęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰e. Koto haunaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰peke laa na loaęž‰me.
\v 17 Tikitiki na piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyaotaęž‰ hoke haue. Pate mo homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na hatuku pulaęž‰ hoke hau make ulaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 18 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ weki wandikimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pa na pitolo ombu halaęž‰me laa hone ulumaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ iki handeteke halaęž‰me ekitaęž‰ mo Hoke Temokomaęž‰ iki hoeyaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Do kenketaęž‰ mo Hoke Temokomaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰pate pa nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki halomaęž‰me laa hone ulumaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 20 Nikaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ niki hone lenkipa witaęž‰laęž‰eki kulu aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ hone ulu polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± hone homeke witolo hataęž‰ pa ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke Yesu Ketiso kone hone homeke wia halomaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰e. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tekee.
\v 21 Yaka wekiwandikio. Mo yayapiki kodaęž‰manu teke paęž‰taęž‰ na hapaęž‰peke. 
